Horror
Discworld ritual help
Horror

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Horror - Creating visions to invoke fear in your targets.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Horror is an offensive ritual, which summons a vision of such fear
that all those affected by it flee in terror, and has the potential
to affect everyone in the room with the priest.  You will need a
holy amulet and two severed hands to perform this ritual.
.EP
